{{see|Guy}}
==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪ|-aɪ]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{informal}} A man.
#:''A new '''guy''' started at the office today.''
# {{informal}} (''in plural'') People, irrespective of their sex(es).
#:''Who are those guys?''
#:''Hey, guys!''
# {{informal}} An object personified, usually used with a demonstrative adjective.
#:''Out of all the computers made today, this '''guy''' is my favorite.''
# {{informal}} A form of address used in Canada and parts of USA.
#:''Hey guy!''
#A support cable used to limit motion. 


